text:
Great effort!
Today's show was awesome!

Was it?
Rather, it isn't like it was even my show.

No no, back dancers are still a part of the show.
It's looks like your lessons as a unit as paying off.

Mm, that's...
I wonder if they are.

Lately, when we've been doing lessons...
It's like... everyone is really serious.
Like, you can't really compose yourself, you know.

No, not reallyー
It's nothingー

...If you say so, I won't pry any further. But if
there's anything troubling you, I'd like you to tell me.
